<p>Saturday 7 Aug. 1915</p>
<p>Sunday 8th Aug. 1915</p>
<p>Appreciably surprised at slovenly style of Church Parade.  No discipline, smoking, talking &amp; general irregularity.  Platoon Sergeants worse than the men.  The whole show simply a parody.</p>
<p>Monday 9th Aug. 1915</p>
<p>Nothing of moment</p>
<p>Tuesday 10th Aug. 1915</p>
<p>Usual routine.</p>
<p>Wednesday 11th Aug. 1915</p>
<p>Usual routine.  Informed of the fall of Achi-Baba (rumour).  Wrote Mab another letter (unfinished).</p>
<p>Thursday 12th Aug. 1915</p>
<p>Warned that we shall leave for the front in 10 days. [text crossed out]</p>
